==English==

===Adjective===
'''jerky'''
# Characterized by physical [[jerking]].

===Noun===
'''jerky'''
# [[Meat]] [[cured]] or [[preserved]] by [[cutting]] into [[thin]] [[strip]]s and [[drying]] in the [[sun]].

===Etymology===
* Quechua ''charqui'' ("char-key" in English): sun-dried or air-dried strips of meat.